title: Arris CMTS: CPU Utilization
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arris
license: GPL
distribution:
description:
 This check monitors the CPU utilization for ech CPU Slot on a arrais cmts devices.

 Please note that the reported utilization alrady is an average value computed by the device.

 You can configure upper levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} (default: 90, 95)

 The service goes {WARN}/{CRIT} if the temperature exceeds these levels.

 The check uses the CADANT-CMTS-EQUIPMENT-MIB.

item:
 If available the identifier of the CPU, otherwise the index of the module.

inventory:
 One service is created for each slot
